{"tid":1614270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（澄清）928爆眼手足","createTime":"2019-10-02T17:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T05:31:38.000Z","uid":242025,"like":122,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c856aa27babe6f8b379350cdb2fa81319986cd","tid":1614270,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:36:35.000Z","msg":"鑒於有幾個post都講緊呢位手足<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WPe5wcF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWPe5wcF.png&h=142afe46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">想澄清返</span><br />\n<br />\n呢位手足無爆到眼，佢只係比狗㩒低咗<br />\n有傳佢被爆眼有可能係因為角度問題<br />\n佢瞓低嗰時有粒催淚彈係佢隔離<br />\n佢無爆到眼<br />\n佢被捕之後係有送院，只係頭部受咗傷，傷縫幾針<br />\n今日有份係西九上庭，亦都獲保釋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/enrrZ67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FenrrZ67.jpg&h=bbff8296&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RCD6fFt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRCD6fFt.jpg&h=394dda8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95Fz80u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95Fz80u.jpg&h=381ed49d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以對返條褲嘅顏色同埋對鞋<br />\n多謝大家咁關心呢位手足<br />\n喺度同大家報個平安<br />\n<br />\n利申：呢位手足係我朋友嘅親戚黎"},{"pid":"4325f5d56d13a74c677aa16596ba025167cd18f8","tid":1614270,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:39:08.000Z","msg":"打錯標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係929"},{"pid":"ca84896ab53989344a7faf116573d8e9ee8e2c1d","tid":1614270,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>928</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c539fc4a4258e77b475a2ff2a7d41a8aa799b796","tid":1614270,"uid":743,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oOVDRgr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l